{"id":196328,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/11/维权网-长沙杨继忠因拆迁补偿不合理自杀（图）/","date":"2011-11-16T18:31:30Z","modified":"2011-11-16T18:31:30Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙杨继忠因拆迁补偿不合理自杀（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-p22FWME77ZM/Tr8xSLNF8WI/AAAAAAAACug/679PRrtQm8c/s1600/B72E87F8BE536FA415535D6E1AF1DEFF965BB497CB1AD00FDFDC521A7B165962F050A2ACC34977D04B080C562DEAB9F0560CCE74EFD40211D4B3FE6D5FF2219BEC6EDA4852D66C09E3A3AE88A3E465376554AB1BD6BD95.jpg\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\">    </a><img border=\"0\" height=\"228\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-p22FWME77ZM/Tr8xSLNF8WI/AAAAAAAACug/679PRrtQm8c/s320/B72E87F8BE536FA415535D6E1AF1DEFF965BB497CB1AD00FDFDC521A7B165962F050A2ACC34977D04B080C562DEAB9F0560CCE74EFD40211D4B3FE6D5FF2219BEC6EDA4852D66C09E3A3AE88A3E465376554AB1BD6BD95.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-yZHHcNLqOec/Tr8xTod-AQI/AAAAAAAACuo/wBi3y56Gg4M/s1600/%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D10.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"216\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-yZHHcNLqOec/Tr8xTod-AQI/AAAAAAAACuo/wBi3y56Gg4M/s320/%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D10.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员姚立法报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日上午七点多</span><span>钟，长沙市梅溪湖乡天顶村坳水塘组</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">43</span><span>岁的男性村民杨继忠跳楼，死在离自家房屋一、二十米远的邻居杨细林家一栋即将要拆除的四层楼房前。这一消息在山村中顿时炸开了锅，同时也引起了政府的迅速反应，不到九点警方就封锁了这一地段，三、四百公安、城管等公职人员以及警车、轿车还有殡仪馆的车把地势本来就不宽敞的山坳围得水泄不通，政府公职人员比村民的人数还多，直到下午五点多钟，尸体被殡仪馆的车拉走，才解除警戒。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据当地村民李建、谭伟芝两位女士介绍，死者今年四十三岁，妻子谭迎宾，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">38</span><span>岁，一身的病，有两个儿女，女儿，杨阳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>岁，儿子杨俊</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 8</span><span>岁，父亲杨玉坚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 70</span><span>岁，母亲罗美双</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 63</span><span>岁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，这一带正在征地拆迁，死者家的房屋有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">700-800</span><span>平米，拆迁办给他家计算的补偿款才</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">46</span><span>万。而死者家的邻居杨细林是本村的会计，房屋是和死者的房屋同时建的，面积差不多，就能补偿几百万。这一极大的差距使死者想不通，多次找大队书记陈建兴、村会计杨细林以及拆迁办理论，无结果，是导致杨继忠跳楼的原因。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨继忠自杀后，政府给家属额外补偿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">32</span><span>万，以示这次自杀死亡事件就此平息。但很多知情村民却因为拆迁过程中的不公正要发出自己的声音。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>李建：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13574196809<span>  </span></span><span>谭伟芝：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15874937380</span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5056176505843305595?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[8937,8906,11955]}